channel.title: I need to know why this happens
channel.description: when im in my own server, when i give my guy the thing si want, i lose connection and cant get back on it with him, i have to make a new one, and i cant join anyones sever, when i try to it just freezes for a bit then it says there was an erroe connecting, tell me why these things happen plz.

item.title: I need to know why this happens
item.dc:creator: @Xbox_Modder Xbox Modder
item.description:
@Xbox_Modder wrote:

The items you are spawning are most likely NOT in your item.cfg therefore it’s loading an invalid item ID… Well, attempting to and when it can’t… It stops loading the account and gives you an error…

Just make sure the item you are adding is in your item.cfg and is compatible with your cache…

Goodluck…
